java.lang.Object

NimProbe
public class NimProbeBase
extends Object

The base class for the probe, containing parts of the probe that does not have to be seen in the probe.

nimAttachProbe

protected NimSessionListener nimAttachProbe(String hubqueuename,
                                            String subject,
                                            NimSessionListener sessionlistenerold,
                                            NimSessionListenerList sessionlistenerlist)
                                     throws NimException
Initiates a subscriber channel to the closest NimBUS Hub. The probe attempts a connection to a fixed queue (same name as probe) using "attach", and defaults to a "subscribe" if the queue does not exist. The new "temporary" sessionlistener is added to the sessionlist

Parameters:
hubqueuename - The hub queue name
subject - The subscription subject
sessionlistenerold - The old sessionlistener if a old one is to be removed
sessionlistenerlist - The list of session listeners
Returns:
The sessionlistener for this "hybrid" session
Throws:
NimException - may be thrown
